- All internal private functions in `deploy.ts` and `revert.ts` (`executeDeployAction`, `createDeployTarget`, `backupExisting`, `removeTarget`, `executeRevertAction`, `lstatOutcome`) — all unchanged
- All existing test assertions — none of the property accesses (`action.skill`, `action.agent`, `action.source`, `action.target`, `action.method`) are removed, only `kind` is added

